    <h2>1. Convection Oven Prices in India — Countertop vs Floor Models</h2>

    <p>The convection oven is the most widely used oven for bakery operations in India, from home bakers to large production facilities. It uses a fan to circulate hot air for even baking — ideal for cakes, pastries, cookies, rusks, puffs, and a huge range of bakery products. Let's break down oven prices by size and origin.</p>

    <h3>Countertop Convection Ovens (4–6 Tray)</h3>

    <p>Countertop models sit on an existing worktable and are the entry point for anyone setting up an oven for bakery use in India. They're compact, affordable, and perfect for small-scale production.</p>

