    <h2>2. Deck Oven Prices in India — 1-Deck Through 4-Deck</h2>

    <p>A deck oven is the second most popular oven for bakery use in India, especially for bakeries that produce bread, baguettes, focaccia, or any product requiring strong bottom heat. The stone or ceramic baking deck radiates heat from below, which is essential for achieving proper crust development and oven spring in artisan breads.</p>

    <p>Deck ovens come in stackable configurations — 1-deck, 2-deck, 3-deck, and 4-deck — with each deck operating as an independent baking chamber. For a detailed comparison with convection ovens, read our <a href="/blog/deck-oven-vs-convection-oven">deck oven vs convection oven</a> guide.</p>

