    <h3>Deck Oven Price List — With Steam Injection</h3>

    <p>Steam injection adds ₹40,000 – ₹1,50,000 to the base price depending on the brand and mechanism. Manual steam (water tray) is cheapest; automatic steam injection with programmable bursts is the most expensive. Steam is critical for professional bread baking — it keeps the crust pliable during the first minutes of baking, allowing the bread to expand fully before the crust hardens.</p>

