    <h2>5. Combi Oven Prices in India — 6, 10 & 20 Tray</h2>

    <p>Combi (combination) ovens combine convection heating, steam injection, and sometimes microwave — all in one unit. They're the most versatile oven for bakery and restaurant kitchens, capable of baking, roasting, steaming, grilling, and more. Combi ovens are popular in hotels, QSR chains, catering companies, and bakeries that also serve food.</p>

    <p>The commercial oven price for combi models is significantly higher than single-function ovens, but the versatility often justifies the investment, especially in space-constrained kitchens.</p>

